  <brief_title>Early FDG PET/CT Imaging as a Measure of Response in Patients With Non-Hodgkin Lymphoma on Lenalidomide</brief_title>
  <official_title>Early FDG PET/CT Imaging as a Measure of Response in Patients With Non-Hodgkin Lymphoma on Lenalidomide</official_title>
  <sponsors>
