  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Adult patients with non-Hodgkin lymphoma who will be treated with lenalidomide will undergo
      FDG PET/CT scan as an early evaluation of response to therapy. Changes in FDG uptake will be
      correlated response and long term outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
